page.title: 17HOUSES AND BUILDINGS
page.content: In our area there are a variety of different buildings. A lot of the area is farmland and there are different sizes of farms. In the villages of Bilton, Sproatley,Thirtleby and Wyton there are different sorts of houses. Most of these houses are semi-detached bungalows.Some of them are cottages. In our area there is a new village hall in Bilton, and there is a village institute in Sproatley. The houses all have gardens. There are two pubs in this area.There are no factories around here. There is a church in Sproatley and chapels in Bilton and Wyton. Also there are no main offices or big stores in the area we had to study for the Project.
